OL,3,CShip's captain jailed for six years
OL,4,Cover fatal North Sea crash
OL,6,FA ship's captain has been jailed for
OL,7,Fsix years following the death of a
OL,8,Fcrewman in a crash with an oil tanker
OL,9,Fin the North Sea.
OL,11,FRussian Vladimir Motin had been on
OL,12,Fsole watch duty when container ship
OL,13,Fthe Solong collided with the Stena
OL,14,FImmaculate anchored near the Humber
OL,15,FEstuary at 9.47am on 10 March last
OL,16,Fyear.
OL,18,FMark Angelo Pernia, who was working on
OL,19,Fthe Solong's bow, died instantly in
OL,20,Fthe fire, although his body was never
OL,21,Frecovered.
