OL,6,FThe Filipino man had a five-year-old
OL,7,Fchild at the time of the collision,
OL,8,Fbut he never met his second child, who
OL,9,Fwas born two months after his death.
OL,11,FAfter an Old Bailey trial, a jury
OL,12,Ffound Motin guilty of manslaughter by
OL,13,Fgross negligence on Monday 2 February.
OL,15,FOn Thursday 5 February he was
OL,16,Fsentenced to six years in prison. He
OL,17,Fwill be eligible for release on
OL,18,Flicense after four years.
