OL,6,FThe basic facts of the collision
OL,7,F"suggest a ship unaware of the ship
OL,8,Fahead" and that was the "most likely"
OL,9,Fexplanation, he said.
OL,11,FThe judge suggested Motin had led
OL,12,Fjurors on a "merry dance" in his
OL,13,Fevidence, which was an "exercise in
OL,14,Finventive distraction".
OL,16,F"His claim to be confused was a lie
OL,17,Fthat unravelled when tested at trial,"
OL,18,Fhe added.
