OL,6,FMotin's explanation that he did not
OL,7,Finitiate a crash stop for fear of
OL,8,Fhitting the accommodation block of the
OL,9,FStena Immaculate was "desperate
OL,10,Fstuff", Mr Justice Baker said.
OL,12,FHe said: "You were a serious accident
OL,13,Fwaiting to happen."
OL,15,FMotin had shown a "blatant disregard
OL,16,Ffor the very high risk of death" and
OL,17,Ffallen prey to his own complacency and
OL,18,Farrogance, the judge said.
