OL,6,FMr Pernia was described by colleagues
OL,7,Fas a friend and had appeared "quietly
OL,8,Fconfident, at ease, a man upon whom
OL,9,Fone might depend", the court heard.
OL,11,FHis death was "wholly avoidable" and
OL,12,Fthe blame lay squarely on the
OL,13,Fdefendant, the judge said.
OL,15,FOther members of the Solong and Stena
OL,16,FImmaculate crew could have died and
OL,17,Fthe crash caused "huge" destruction of
OL,18,Fthe cargo, he added.
