OL,6,FThe senior judge said Motin's account
OL,7,Fwas "highly implausible", adding his
OL,8,Fexplanation he did not initiate a
OL,9,Fcrash stop for fear of hitting the
OL,10,Faccommodation block of the Stena
OL,11,FImmaculate was "desperate stuff".
OL,13,FIn a victim impact statement read to
OL,14,Fthe court, Mr Pernia's widow Leacel
OL,15,Fsaid no amount of compensation made up
OL,16,Ffor the "pain" of her loss and the
OL,17,Fimpact on her young family.
