OL,6,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,7,FDetective Chief Superintendent Craig
OL,8,FNicholson said: "Motin completely
OL,9,Ffailed in this duty as a Captain,
OL,10,Fcausing the death of one of his own
OL,11,Fcrew and endangering the remaining
OL,12,Flives of the crews of both vessels.
OL,14,F"Motin has shown no remorse at any
OL,15,Fstage of the investigation or court
OL,16,Fproceedings, and even though he has
OL,17,Fnow been sentenced and held
OL,18,Faccountable for his crimes, it will
OL,19,Fnot bring Mark back.
